msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "Nintendo - Game Boy / Color (Gearboy)"
msgstr "Nintendo - Game Boy / Color (Gearboy)"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "Gearboy is a Nintendo Game Boy / Game Boy Color emulator that runs on iOS, Raspberry Pi, Mac, Windows, Linux and RetroArch."
msgstr "Gearboy je emulátor Nintendo Game Boy / Game Boy Color pro iOS, Raspberry Pi, Mac, Windows, Linux a RetroArch."

